I have been reading about ppl griping about sorcies and I must say I am pretty happy with my sorc.  He is level 36 with Mind at 2/3 and rest of points split between Matter/Body.  Once I have Mind up to 34 I was planning on dumping the rest of my point to Body but may wait now from the things I have read below about changes to Matter.  <P>Anyway, my question is this....How about letting our pets zone with us?  Seems like such a minor fix and would make a HUGE diffrence to the career of a sorc.   From leveling (only 2 dungeons on Albion have charmable pets class mobs), to PvP, and especially grouping.   With such a limited number of charmable mobs, allowing them to zone with us would make life a hell of alot easier.  As far as I am concerned the rest of the sorc is working fine at my current lvl.<P><BR>Thanks,<P>Oracles
